ocoaPods Specs repository and Swift Package repository is ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"private"}]},{"text":" and granted via SSH.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"To request access, please generate an SSH key pair and send the public key to our team. We’ll provision access to the appropriate repositories.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"anchor":"1-Manual-Installation","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"1. Manual Installation"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Manually install the provided "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PSReaderUI.xcframework"},{"type":"text","text":" and its dependencies by dragging and dropping them into your Xcode project."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"PSReaderUI.xcframework","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"PSReader.xcframework"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"PDFNet.xcframework"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tools.xcframework"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Ensure the frameworks are set to ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Embed and Sign"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" in your Xcode project settings.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"2-CocoaPods","level":3,"text":"2. CocoaPods"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Specs repository:"}]}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["git@bitbucket.org:pagesuite\/psreader-specs.git"]},{"type":"aside","name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": The Apryse SDK integration is slightly non-standard. We recommend pinning it to version ","type